n Truth Four Realms' 4x3 matrix spread to pierce illusions versus truth. It details the spread rows: his world, your world, relationship illusions, truth layer, each with precise positions. Justification follows: this spread fits perfectly for their acting, projections, and buried truths. Finally, it provides an example of potential truths if drawn now."
